# Docker environment variables have been split per service.
# See:
#   .env.server.example   — variables for the ocr-lab-server container
#   .env.frontend.example — variables for the ocr-lab-frontend container
#
# The root .env file is still used for docker compose ${VAR} interpolation
# (e.g. CSRF_TRUSTED_ORIGINS for the build arg, TAG for image tagging).
# See docs/deployment.md for details.
